# Project Rules

- we use gluestack-ui v2, we already installed all components which located in the @/components/ui
- we use nativewind
- we use typescript
- we use moti for animations
- we use expo
- we use lucide-react-native for icons
- we follow Modern Minimal design principles

# Design Guidelines

- Use solid backgrounds with thin borders (0.5px)
- Keep consistent border radius (rounded-xl)
- Use semantic colors (primary for actions, error for alerts)
- Maintain clean typography and spacing
- Keep interactions subtle and purposeful

