# Dangerous behavior

- when creating new files, ask user to get permission to create the file

# Styling Guidelines

- Use HStack and VStack for layout instead of View or Box
- HStack and VStack props: space (string) and reversed (boolean)
- Use nativewind classes for styling instead of inline styles
- Let gluestack handle theming
